OL,3,CFamilies condemn decision not to
OL,4,Cprosecute care home staff over Covid
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FRelatives of seven elderly residents
OL,8,Fwho died after contracting coronavirus
OL,9,Fat a nursing home during the pandemic
OL,10,Fhave condemned the decision not to
OL,11,Fprosecute anyone, an inquest heard.
OL,13,FThe families spoke out after hearing
OL,14,Fthat the manager of the Holmesley Care
OL,15,FHome in Sidford, Devon, and a nurse
OL,16,Fhad been arrested and interviewed by
OL,17,Fpolice following the Covid outbreak,
OL,18,Fbut were not charged.
