OL,3,CFamilies condemn decision not to
OL,4,Cprosecute care home staff over Covid
OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThey were questioned following the
OL,8,Fdeaths of William Wilkinson, 102,
OL,9,FDoris Lockett, 92, Roy Gilliam, 96,
OL,10,FJean Hartley, 81, Susan Skinner, 70,
OL,11,FRonald Bampfylde, 92, and Stanislawa
OL,12,FKoch, 93, all of whom died in March or
OL,13,FApril 2021.
OL,15,FThe inquest in Exeter has heard
OL,16,Fallegations that during the pandemic
OL,17,Fsome staff did not wear face masks or
OL,18,FPPE, that others carried on working
OL,19,Fafter testing positive for the virus,
OL,20,Fand that test results were ignored.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/12
