OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FA detective told the hearing that the
OL,8,Ftwo staff members ` manager Joanne
OL,9,FBurchell and nurse Christos
OL,10,FProvistallis ` had been arrested on
OL,11,Fsuspicion of ill-treatment or wilful
OL,12,Fneglect, but the Crown Prosecution
OL,13,FService decided there was not a
OL,14,Frealistic prospect of conviction.
OL,16,FIt has been alleged that Mr
OL,17,FProvistallis had refused to wear a
OL,18,Fface mask after claiming "Covid was a
OL,19,Fconspiracy" ` but later ended up in a
OL,20,Fhospital's intensive care unit after
OL,21,Fcontracting the virus.
