OL,7,FOthers alleged Mrs Burchell had not
OL,8,Fsent sick staff home due to shortages
OL,9,Fand had ignored positive lateral flow
OL,10,Ftests results.
OL,12,FWladek Koch, whose mother died,
OL,13,Fsuggested the authorities did not have
OL,14,Fthe "courage" to prosecute and drew
OL,15,Fcomparisons with people receiving
OL,16,Ffixed penalty notices for breaching
OL,17,Fthe Covid-19 regulations.
