OL,7,F"If they had done the honourable thing
OL,8,Fthat would have set a precedent. As it
OL,9,Fis now, there is a licence for people
OL,10,Fto do exactly the same again and get
OL,11,Faway with it," he said.
OL,13,F"And not even a #100 fine. Does no-one
OL,14,Frealise how disgusting this is, and
OL,15,Fjust passing on condolences is a gross
OL,16,Finsult given there have been no
OL,17,Fsanctions levied against these two
OL,18,Fpeople who did so much ill?"
OL,26,@oD@AOUsD@NO]zD@\OU
