OL,5,Cdeaths
OL,7,FThe fact is this could happen again as
OL,8,Fthe police and the CPS don't consider
OL,9,Fthe evidence adequate to do anything
OL,10,Fabout it and they get off Scot-free
OL,11,Fwhile people's lives were sacrificed."
OL,13,FSally Burns, the daughter of Mr
OL,14,FBampfylde, said: "I am absolutely
OL,15,Fastounded by all of this.
OL,17,F"It is just a litany of processes,
OL,18,Finvestigations and recommendations and
OL,19,Fthis, that and the other that everyone
OL,20,Fcan ignore, and nothing happens at the
OL,21,Fend of it except people die.
