OL,7,F"I don't at the moment have the words
OL,8,Fto formulate a question. It's just
OL,9,Fstaggering, I am not surprised, but to
OL,10,Fhear it all condensed in just one week
OL,11,Fis just horrific."
OL,13,FAlison Shaw, who is the sister of Ms
OL,14,FSkinner, said: "Now knowing what
OL,15,Fhappened and hearing it stated and
OL,16,Fproven, I am actually also quite
OL,17,Fshocked that potentially there will be
OL,18,Fno repercussions on the people who I
OL,19,Ffeel were responsible.
