OL,7,F"My sister described chaos and staff
OL,8,Fshouting at each other and just things
OL,9,Ffalling apart. That wasn't just during
OL,10,Fthe Covid-19 time, but prior to that
OL,11,Fas well.
OL,13,F"She felt there was something innately
OL,14,Fwrong in there and she had actually
OL,15,Fworked at Holmesley some time.
OL,17,F"I think the communication between us
OL,18,Fall had it been better might have made
OL,19,Fsome difference at some point and I
OL,20,Fpersonally feel bad about that.
