OL,7,FGiving evidence, Detective Sergeant
OL,8,FTom Hall said charges of gross
OL,9,Fnegligence manslaughter were quickly
OL,10,Fruled out against Mrs Burchell and
OL,11,Fnurse Christos Provistallis and
OL,12,Finstead the investigation focused on
OL,13,Fill-treatment.
OL,15,F"It was an untested area of law at the
OL,16,Ftime, and we didn't have any pandemic-
OL,17,Frelated case law that we could refer
OL,18,Fto," the officer said.
